{"tid":1031062,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［難題］到底邊條路最快去到荃灣","createTime":"2019-02-21T11:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T00:44:04.000Z","uid":126697,"like":2,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6799ef4b2a9b657e02919b73bd100b6c90bd68a1","tid":1031062,"uid":126697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3NsbiBn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3NsbiBn.png&h=fb648afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當荃灣係目的地，邊條路最快到達<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">16個站荃灣線坐到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">9個站連埋行路時間轉線東涌線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n有冇人實測過"},{"pid":"155f7a4a97ddcd60e6132c748c052d705faa2230","tid":1031062,"uid":120053,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:47:02.000Z","msg":"搭930最快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecafc445521e831b6f40ecdfbb7a2675b617039","tid":1031062,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:48:16.000Z","msg":"隨意門最快"},{"pid":"bfa5151e3cc34e981fe391dc7c96ab917d3cfd7c","tid":1031062,"uid":37297,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:49:14.000Z","msg":"起點呢"},{"pid":"239e8d546f96802804260522588d123bc02e0413","tid":1031062,"uid":209391,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:49:40.000Z","msg":"16個站 <br />\n利申：每日都搭"},{"pid":"9aed8ca58771e6c2be812260b6528b02821ba496","tid":1031062,"uid":225916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"239e8d546f96802804260522588d123bc02e0413","tid":1031062,"uid":209391,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:49:40.000Z","msg":"16個站 <br />\n利申：每日都搭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:53:28.000Z","msg":"如果你跑得快過小明 9秒9跑到香港站<br />\n再加上唔洗等車 應該可以倒贏有找<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過如果你都跑得快過小明又做咩要搭車呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d6b539b6a911d3947c5ddab51504bd8d79ca3c","tid":1031062,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:56:19.000Z","msg":"btw 除非你起點係中環，如果唔係要係中環轉荃灣線會輸好多時間(所以係港島線要轉一定係金鐘轉車)"},{"pid":"d5394d88d757ab2c895a72bc8178ddd168ef3ec9","tid":1031062,"uid":33433,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"155f7a4a97ddcd60e6132c748c052d705faa2230","tid":1031062,"uid":120053,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T11:47:02.000Z","msg":"搭930最快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:02:45.000Z","msg":"930x仲快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ec7167544fc69894f03268d3f06d1af22d5a16","tid":1031062,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:10:17.000Z","msg":"有年去荃灣拜年我兩個表哥實測過<br />\n結果係搭荃灣線果個快d到"},{"pid":"175ca7ec858e0131d58c6e088a2e4c12089469ac","tid":1031062,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14ec7167544fc69894f03268d3f06d1af22d5a16","tid":1031062,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:10:17.000Z","msg":"有年去荃灣拜年我兩個表哥實測過<br />\n結果係搭荃灣線果個快d到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:12:36.000Z","msg":"但你係中環站轉咁一定慢d 搭完港島線都唔會係中環轉啦"},{"pid":"a844898cdf2b6aba53b4bc0b7bc867e1d8636773","tid":1031062,"uid":34383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:39:15.000Z","msg":"放工時間 你等兩~三次車先逼到入去上紅線"},{"pid":"89fc8d9e9c95922e60d865c1353c6c843dac81a7","tid":1031062,"uid":34383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a844898cdf2b6aba53b4bc0b7bc867e1d8636773","tid":1031062,"uid":34383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:39:15.000Z","msg":"放工時間 你等兩~三次車先逼到入去上紅線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:39:34.000Z","msg":"如果係金鐘"},{"pid":"118e55c4cdfba283e55b593094bd26cf11cb4e3b","tid":1031062,"uid":136002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T18:53:22.000Z","msg":"搭開橙色<br />\n至少人少啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c34c795744b6658fde2f1ca348c90f737513d42","tid":1031062,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T19:04:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29f3abb04735672388c12542402f82ee75b54916","tid":1031062,"uid":4519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T19:12:16.000Z","msg":"睇你起點係中環定香港，終點係荃灣定荃灣西，因為有步行時間<br />\n剩計車程最快係香港橙色線，荃灣西紫色線"},{"pid":"ea00344a58d7ed563c81847ec31d00ca11ca67e4","tid":1031062,"uid":10672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T19:15:51.000Z","msg":"其實係睇你係中環行過去有幾快"},{"pid":"2e9841e52a65208f453630ab9683a50869c0a366","tid":1031062,"uid":181706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T20:20:57.000Z","msg":"我金鍾番工 步行到青衣番工收工 ps 住海濱 我都係睇情況邊頭近 荃灣或荃灣西落"},{"pid":"5b3df9207280dd7cb189e32d00c9f30c096e573d","tid":1031062,"uid":17184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T20:31:51.000Z","msg":"假設中環站起步，荃灣站終點<br />\n橙線坐到荔景站轉紅線到荃灣站，如無意外應該係最快，因為坐到南昌站轉西鐵綫到荃灣西站，再行返去荃灣站起碼都要10-15分鐘"},{"pid":"484b58ac8981db5d003ed2f964c87dc0a123e41d","tid":1031062,"uid":4155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T21:16:08.000Z","msg":"而家要睇你個人近中環站定香港站<br />\n以前東涌線未有南昌果陣好撚快<br />\nbtw我都係會揀搭930/930x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55feafd1263dc3c2f2c3ac7aeb96cd3164fe4371","tid":1031062,"uid":192746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e9841e52a65208f453630ab9683a50869c0a366","tid":1031062,"uid":181706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T20:20:57.000Z","msg":"我金鍾番工 步行到青衣番工收工 ps 住海濱 我都係睇情況邊頭近 荃灣或荃灣西落"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T21:54:26.000Z","msg":"海濱我揀龍德街行翻去，同荃西行翻去差唔多"},{"pid":"21917b039a918f056d97974d1b876f5b7d5d88e6","tid":1031062,"uid":47659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T18:47:38.000Z","msg":"就算你中環去香港站行得幾快<br />\n東涌線班次疏都係事實"},{"pid":"8cdae43e6108374f2f2be9d85bd52c13ca281213","tid":1031062,"uid":3441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T03:41:02.000Z","msg":"930X is the solution <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edeacb16cdd2bbde8c47437153b5dd78866f919e","tid":1031062,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T04:50:34.000Z","msg":"如果由銅鑼灣去荃灣站呢 (假設金鐘站好多人)？<br />\n<br />\n1. 搭港島線到金鐘轉荃灣線去荃灣，喺金鐘月台慢慢迫上車<br />\n2. 搭港島線到中環轉荃灣線去荃灣<br />\n3. 搭港島線到金鐘轉荃灣線去中環，去到中環唔落車再原車去荃灣<br />\n4. 搭港島線到中環再行去香港站搭東涌線，再喺荔景轉荃灣線去荃灣"},{"pid":"57964788ea48d1dcb81f89021017f52b765d7354","tid":1031062,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edeacb16cdd2bbde8c47437153b5dd78866f919e","tid":1031062,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T04:50:34.000Z","msg":"如果由銅鑼灣去荃灣站呢 (假設金鐘站好多人)？<br />\n<br />\n1. 搭港島線到金鐘轉荃灣線去荃灣，喺金鐘月台慢慢迫上車<br />\n2. 搭港島線到中環轉荃灣線去荃灣<br />\n3. 搭港島線到金鐘轉荃灣線去中環，去到中環唔落車再原車去荃灣<br />\n4. 搭港島線到中環再行去香港站搭東涌線，再喺荔景轉荃灣線去荃灣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T02:59:35.000Z","msg":"5. 搭930X"},{"pid":"49d54cb63137bffc5ac4292013a43b1209ff1982","tid":1031062,"uid":143768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T00:44:04.000Z","msg":"樓主果然做乜柒都要快"}]}